        },
        {
            "title": "財經｜據報軟銀、NEC、本田及索尼成立開發國產AI新公司",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜據報軟銀、NEC、本田及索尼成立開發國產AI新公司\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nvJ6N1NDpC3.YMtrx76erg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜據報軟銀、NEC、本田及索尼成立開發國產<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"AI\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:AI;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/AI\">AI</a>新公司</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日媒報道，以軟銀、NEC、本田及索尼為主企業已成立人工智能開發的新公司。在美國和中國企業開發領先的背景下，該公司將利用日本政府的支援打造國產AI基礎模型以實現反超前，設想將開發的AI提供給日本企業。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司名為「日本AI基礎模型開發」，計劃彙集約100名AI開發人員，目標在2030年以前開發出參數規模達約1萬億的大型AI基礎模型，成為日本國內最具規模的AI之一，且將開放給出資企業以外的日本企業使用。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-61f3d603-65e4-3692-955c-faf121a68042-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當中，軟銀和NEC將進行開發，本田及索尼則把開發成果用於自動駕駛。AI開發企業Preferred Networks亦有參與。開發的AI也會向出資企業以外的日企廣泛開放，未來還將涉足操控機械人的AI領域。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT Telegram: <br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2M63TRO;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2M63TRO</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT YouTube channel:<br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2FgJTen;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FgJTen</a></p></div>",
